PrecisApproval of an application made by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE D'ASBESTOS, duly incorporated in Quebec and registered in 1973, to change (a) its name to "Chambre de commerce de la région d'Asbestos", and (b) the boundaries of its district to include Wotton, St-Georges de Windsor, Trois-Lacs, St-Adrien, St-Camille and Ham-Sud.
Attachments
precis:
Approval of an application made by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE D'ASBESTOS, duly
incorporated in Quebec and registered in 1973, to change (a) its name to
"Chambre de commerce de la région d'Asbestos", and (b) the boundaries of
its district to include Wotton, St-Georges de Windsor, Trois-Lacs,
St-Adrien, St-Camille and Ham-Sud.
